WEBVTT

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:30.960
lakini pia na nguvu hafifu ya sumaku
umeme,na nguvu za nguvu za nuklia

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:33.716
ambayo inashikilia atomu na nuklia
pamoja.

00:02:33.716 --> 00:02:34.566
Matokeo yake,

00:02:34.566 --> 00:02:38.806
mata inayotengeneza nyota
inavunjika katika vipande vidogo.

00:02:38.806 --> 00:02:42.227
Hata atomu na vipande vidogo vya
atomu vitaharibika.

00:02:42.227 --> 00:02:44.967
Hiyo ni Mraruo Mkubwa.

00:02:44.967 --> 00:02:46.607
Vipi kuhusu tukio la tatu,

00:02:46.607 --> 00:02:48.877
ambapo kamba ya mpira inashinda?

00:02:48.877 --> 00:02:51.577
Ambayo ina shabihiana na uwezekano
wa mbeleni

00:02:51.577 --> 00:02:55.917
ambapo nguvu ya uvutano inaletea kusambaa
kwa ulimwengu kusimama---

00:02:55.917 --> 00:02:58.195
Halafu inaigeuza.

00:02:58.195 --> 00:03:01.005
Galaksi zitaanza kukimbizana kukaribiana,